704201f-b.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - 5th Avenue
704201f-b.text:
Flatbush Avenue, at the intersection of Fifth Avenue, viewing north up the former and showing the B. M. T. elevated line thereon. The trolley is turning in and is continuing down Fifth Avenue. Across the "El" is the Williamsburg Savings Pank
Building.
View 2 shows the gas statfon at the intersection of Flntbush and Fifth Avenues (right, view 1) andd the rears of seversl rookeries fronting on Atlantic Avenue. Flatbush Avenue is on the left and the Williamsburg Savings Bank Building in
the background.
Views 1,2
June 14, 1940
P. L. Sperr
